Key Match Events: The Washington Nationals had the New York Mets starter Tylor Megill on the ropes in the third inning, putting runners on first and third with no outs, but they could score only one run.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The New York Mets have won back-to-back games against the Washington Nationals.
The Washington Nationals will travel to Chicago to face the Chicago Cubs for a four-game series, concluding their final road trip of the 2024 season.
